data.description: SUBTO OPPORTUNITY!!! This seller is considering SUBTO OFFERS !! Take advantage of a 4.125% interest rate with ALMOST NO MONEY DOWN! Conveniently located on one of the most quiet streets within the guard gated community of Green Valley Estates, this opulent custom home features over 6,000 square feet. Boasting a newly designed kitchen with modern finishes that boost both style and functionality. The flexible floor plan offers two spacious primary bedrooms on the first and second floor. An oversized 6th bedroom can easily be used for an additional family room or media room. The backyard is sure to entertain offering a pool, spa and slide, sport court, built in BBQ and plenty of space for relaxation. Zoned for some of the most highly sought after schools in the valley and situated just minutes from the freeway, and The District. Come see your new home today!
